➜宁夏中卫：苹果飘香采摘忙
http://www.sohu.com/a/418919175_114731	1940
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200917/98f24fd6fbec416b8c3fb8c9d889faef.jpeg" width="500" height="291" /></p>
